high_descs: Turn left, face the knife on the counter, left of the fridge.
Pick up the knife on the counter, closest to the fridge.
Turn around, bring the knife to the counter across the kitchen, turn right to face the bread on the counter.
Open the cabinet under the bread on the counter, put the knife in the mug in there.
Pick up the mug with knife in it.
Turn around, bring the mug to the sink on the right.
Put the mug with knife in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a knife in it, in the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the edge of the kitchen table on your left.
Grab the knife off the table.
Walk to the kitchen table behind you, facing the loaf of bread.
Open the lower-right drawer and place the knife inside the cup.
Grab the cup with the knife in it.
Go to the kitchen sink.
Place the cup and knife inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Gather a knife and cup to place in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and face the counter to the left of the fridge.
Pick up the knife closest to you.
Turn around and walk to the counter with the loaf of bread, look down at the cupboard below the counter.
Open the cupboard door, place the knife inside of the cup inside the cupboard.
Pick up the cup from the cupboard and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the right.
Place the cup in the sink to the left of the head of lettuce.
anns.task_desc: To put a knife and cup in the sink.
